{"tid":313671,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[單親家庭入]自己/父母離婚嘅原因","createTime":"2017-07-08T14:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T16:29:14.000Z","uid":110122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79119e19b7fbb8c90020f6d0429cc7ba59b18a57","tid":313671,"uid":110122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:11:35.000Z","msg":"身邊有唔少朋友家庭都係單親<br />\n冇離婚而又好恩愛嘅真係好少<br />\n有好多就係根本冇哂感情 但因為子女而冇分開<br />\n(好多老豆都比老母怒屌，但死忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n如題 分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋你地覺得父母單親，對你地成長有咩影響？<br />\n<br />\n我自己就單親跟啊媽住，但老豆成日會返嚟煮飯，又會一齊去旅行，所以冇乜影響"},{"pid":"00e74e0ee500ce6d742f4e1e710600939e87f991","tid":313671,"uid":110122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:12:39.000Z","msg":"第一次開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab82a23b5d565b955951e220b5d09b31b217ea9d","tid":313671,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:27:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5c2a8c526b3525df1aacdd524d317ae40b28cd7","tid":313671,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:45:50.000Z","msg":"自己幸福家庭R人講自己幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ff40f4c7a7f467ae98c06bc291895a15c53e33","tid":313671,"uid":110122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T15:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己幸福家庭R人講自己幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係問下有冇影響 冇話一定係負面影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上有d friend嘅父母一齊住真係仲衰過分開"},{"pid":"fdb1181af57702145fb8994c30840deb50b64ffb","tid":313671,"uid":46483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"香港地咪又係因為錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3317aee24d79